        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"hs_h1\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"72042\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/hs_h1/48/54080_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> hs_h1:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I wonder why this function is not available</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Probably because it would result in a lot of unnecessary message overhead and spam-like behavior. Why do you think this would be a good feature? What is the problem with sending images in a single message?</p>",
